-- Lukoil Shareholders Approve Interim Dividend Plan, Interfax Says
-- B y   T o r r e y   C l a r k
-- 2012-06-27T09:46:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-27/lukoil-shareholders-approve-interim-dividend-plan-interfax-says.html
OAO Lukoil’s shareholders approved
changes to the Russian oil producer’s charter, allowing the
payment of interim dividends for each quarter through the year,
Interfax reported, citing the vote at an annual meeting today.  Lukoil will decide in the third quarter on paying a
dividend from its first-half results, Interfax said earlier,
citing Deputy Chief Executive Officer  Leonid Fedun .  To contact the reporter on this story:
